1. http://projects.spring.io/spring-batch/

2. https://docs.spring.io/spring-batch/trunk/reference/html/index.html

api: https://docs.spring.io/spring-batch/trunk/apidocs/index.html

3. EnableBatchProcessing会自动注入如下bean(见 SimpleBatchConfiguration)

JobRepository - bean name "jobRepository"

JobLauncher - bean name "jobLauncher"

JobRegistry - bean name "jobRegistry"

PlatformTransactionManager - bean name "transactionManager"

JobBuilderFactory - bean name "jobBuilders"

StepBuilderFactory - bean name "stepBuilders"

5. default BatchConfigurer the context must contain no more thanone DataSource

https://stackoverflow.com/questions/25540502/use-of-multiple-datasources-in-spring-batch

6. https://spring.io/guides/gs/batch-processing/

7. http://blog.jobbole.com/109857/
